Dragonblood Chymist											KEY:Alchemist Archetype ~ Dragonblood Chymist	CATEGORY:Archetype				TYPE:Archetype.AlchemistArchetype																																		PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=1				PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Alchemist Archetype ~ Dragonblood Chymist],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Alchemist_Archetype_Mutagen=True,Alchemist_Archetype_Discovery2=True,Alchemist_Archetype_Discovery12=True,Alchemist_Archetype_Discovery16=True,Alchemist_Archetype_ThrowAnything=True,Alchemist_Archetype_PoisonResistance=True,Alchemist_Archetype_PoisonUse=True,Alchemist_Archetype_SwiftPoisoning=True]																																																																																																												DESCISPI:YES				DESC:For alchemists, the key to effective mixtures lies in potent ingredients, and what could be more formidable than the blood of wyrms? The dragonblood chymists of Kaer Maga specialize in the reckless distillation of extracts and elixirs that allow them to experience the might of a dragon, however dangerous it might be.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragonblood Chymist ~ Dragonblood Mutagen|PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragonblood Chymist ~ Explosive Breath|PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragonblood Chymist ~ Draconic Resistances|PRECLASS:1,Alchemist=2																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								