Draconic Shaman												KEY:Shaman Archetype ~ Draconic Shaman		CATEGORY:Archetype				TYPE:Archetype.ShamanArchetype																																		PRECLASS:1,Shaman=1				PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Shaman Archetype ~ Draconic Shaman],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Shaman_Archetype_Spirit=True,Shaman_Archetype_SpiritAnimal=True,Shaman_Archetype_Hex4=True,Shaman_Archetype_Hex10=True,Shaman_Archetype_SpiritMagic=True]																																																																																																																																					DESCISPI:YES				DESC:In some regions of Tian Xia, shamans are unusually common, and may have strong ties to dragon gods and imperial dragons who act as mentors. Some of these shamans draw their powers from the might of dragons, rather than from spirits. These shamans each gain a powerful drake as an ally, and view caring for that drake as a sacred duty.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Draconic Shaman ~ Drake Companion|PRECLASS:1,Shaman=1																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.24																																																																																											