Draconic Rage												KEY:Wyrm Singer ~ Draconic Rage			CATEGORY:Special Ability			TYPE:Skald Class Features.WyrmSingerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																DEFINE:WyrmSingerSaveBonus|0	DEFINE:WyrmSingerCombatBonus|0																																																													DESC:A wyrm singer can kindle an echo of ancient rage felt between warring dragon clans in his allies. This ability acts as inspired rage, except those affected gain a +%1 morale bonus on melee attack and damage rolls and a +%2 morale bonus on saving throws against paralysis and sleep effects (but they still take a 1 penalty to their AC), rather than inspired rage's normal bonuses.|WyrmSingerCombatBonus|WyrmSingerSaveBonus																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									BONUS:VAR|WyrmSingerCombatBonus|2	BONUS:VAR|WyrmSingerCombatBonus|SkaldLVL/8	BONUS:VAR|WyrmSingerSaveBonus|2	BONUS:VAR|WyrmSingerSaveBonus|SkaldLVL/4																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.14
Wyrm Saga													KEY:Wyrm Singer ~ Wyrm Saga				CATEGORY:Special Ability			TYPE:Skald Class Features.WyrmSingerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																							DESC:A wyrm singer embraces the essence of the draconic histories, allowing his allies to manifest aspects of a dragon in their physical forms. The wyrm singer selects a single ally within 60 feet to take on a draconic aspect (as per form of the dragon I) of a type of the wyrm singer's choice. The ally cannot use the breath weapon attack provided by form of the dragon. The wyrm singer must expend 1 round of raging song each round to maintain wyrm saga, and can affect only a single ally at a time.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.14
Breath Weapon												KEY:Wyrm Singer ~ Breath Weapon			CATEGORY:Special Ability			TYPE:Skald Class Features.WyrmSingerClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																							DESC:Once per day as a swift action, a wyrm singer can grant a breath weapon attack to himself or an ally affected by his draconic rage raging song. Using the breath weapon is a standard action, and it affects creatures in a 30-foot cone or a 60-foot line. The breath weapons deals %1d6 points of damage, and is of an energy type of the wyrm singer's choice (acid, cold, electricity, or fire). Creatures caught in the area can attempt a Reflex save (DC %2) to halve the damage.|SkaldLVL/2|10+SkaldLVL/2+CHA																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.14

